00:24:53,010 --> 00:24:53,700
All the goods are here.

574
00:25:09,330 --> 00:25:09,900
No need for that.

575
00:25:10,770 --> 00:25:12,090
I have full trust in you

576
00:25:12,460 --> 00:25:13,460
as my client.

577
00:25:14,770 --> 00:25:15,660
I assume your salt

578
00:25:16,220 --> 00:25:17,250
is measured fairly and precisely.

579
00:25:17,940 --> 00:25:19,620
Since you're a valuable client,

580
00:25:20,010 --> 00:25:20,730
allow me to see you off.

581
00:25:21,620 --> 00:25:22,290
No need

582
00:25:22,700 --> 00:25:23,700
for courtesies between us.

583
00:25:24,730 --> 00:25:25,180
Farewell.

584
00:25:43,460 --> 00:25:44,460
Stay where you are!

585
00:25:44,770 --> 00:25:45,140
Go!

586
00:25:45,900 --> 00:25:47,330
Arrest everyone on both sides!

