00:26:05,940 --> 00:26:07,420
of embezzling river transport fees.

589
00:26:08,180 --> 00:26:09,770
Wu Youjing is a prudent man.

590
00:26:10,140 --> 00:26:10,860
Once he sees it,

591
00:26:11,420 --> 00:26:13,180
he will surely shut down
all the transportation of salt himself.

592
00:26:15,420 --> 00:26:16,290
He'll be desperate

593
00:26:16,860 --> 00:26:18,250
[To the Court of Judicial Review]
to find an alternative.

594
00:26:18,730 --> 00:26:19,180
Ping'an,

595
00:26:19,900 --> 00:26:21,530
we can then make our next move.

596
00:26:22,570 --> 00:26:23,490
Prince of Kangping,

597
00:26:23,980 --> 00:26:25,330
I will redeem myself.

598
00:26:25,460 --> 00:26:25,770
Leave!

599
00:26:26,380 --> 00:26:26,730
Yes, sir.

600
00:26:27,330 --> 00:26:28,490
I'm going to find a new source of salt

601
00:26:28,700 --> 00:26:29,620
to make up for my mistake.

602
00:26:31,700 --> 00:26:32,490
Are you really

603
00:26:32,980 --> 00:26:34,180
only asking for 100 wen per dou?

604
00:26:35,660 --> 00:26:36,940
Since Wu Xian'er considers me

605
00:26:36,980 --> 00:26:37,860
a worthy opponent,

606
00:26:38,380 --> 00:26:40,010
I shall grant her wish

607
00:26:40,860 --> 00:26:41,980
and turn into a mouse,

608
00:26:42,940 --> 00:26:44,860
letting her think
she has the upper hand

609
00:26:45,420 --> 00:26:47,940
while delivering this cat

610
00:26:48,420 --> 00:26:49,290
right where I want it.

611
00:26:50,020 --> 00:26:54,090
[Psychiatric Commissioner]

612
00:26:54,090 --> 00:26:56,010
[Imperial]
So, what was left in the jar a year ago

613
00:26:56,090 --> 00:26:57,290
was the token
of the Psychiatric Commissioner.

614
00:26:58,570 --> 00:27:00,380
Miss Ye, since you have returned
to the capital

615
00:27:00,490 --> 00:27:01,490
and come to me,

616
00:27:01,730 --> 00:27:03,700
you must be here
for something important.

617
00:27:04,140 --> 00:27:05,050
There is an official

618
00:27:05,460 --> 00:27:06,250
in the capital

619
00:27:06,490 --> 00:27:08,140
manipulating the salt trade
for personal gain.

620
00:27:08,900 --> 00:27:10,900
I intend to lure out this big fish.

621
00:27:11,250 --> 00:27:12,250
Salt prices have soared,

622
00:27:12,860 --> 00:27:14,250
leaving the people unable to afford it

623
00:27:14,730 --> 00:27:15,770
and struggling to survive.

624
00:27:16,620 --> 00:27:17,810
It's time to expose

625
00:27:18,530 --> 00:27:20,250
the culprit behind this.

626
00:27:25,490 --> 00:27:26,090
Miss Wu,

627
00:27:26,330 --> 00:27:27,250
I received a secret letter

628
00:27:27,810 --> 00:27:28,570
accusing you,

629
00:27:28,620 --> 00:27:30,090
a court official,

630
00:27:30,420 --> 00:27:31,460
of knowingly breaking the law

631
00:27:32,090 --> 00:27:33,490
by using silver
to purchase illegal salt.

632
00:27:33,940 --> 00:27:34,730
Mr. Zhao,

633
00:27:34,900 --> 00:27:35,660
you've arrived just in time.

634
00:27:36,140 --> 00:27:37,140
I also received a secret letter

635
00:27:37,420 --> 00:27:37,860
claiming

636
00:27:38,250 --> 00:27:40,250
that illegal salt was being traded here.

637
00:27:40,490 --> 00:27:41,420
So I came to make a deal

638
00:27:41,700 --> 00:27:42,490
and draw them out.

639
00:27:42,980 --> 00:27:43,490
Sure enough,

640
00:27:44,570 --> 00:27:46,010
we caught them red-handed.

641
00:27:46,530 --> 00:27:47,290
Please, Mr. Zhao,

642
00:27:47,770 --> 00:27:48,620
take her into custody.

643
00:27:49,940 --> 00:27:50,620
Mr. Zhao,

644
00:27:51,380 --> 00:27:52,860
Miss Wu accuses me
of selling illegal salt,

645
00:27:53,330 --> 00:27:54,490
but buying and selling
are equally punishable.

646
00:27:54,940 --> 00:27:55,900
The silver is right here as proof.

647
00:27:56,140 --> 00:27:57,460
How can I be convicted

648
00:27:57,860 --> 00:27:58,860
based on her words alone?

649
00:28:16,770 --> 00:28:17,380
Sir,

650
00:28:17,530 --> 00:28:18,420
we've found a set
of Mountain-Pattern Armor.

651
00:28:29,220 --> 00:28:29,700
Miss Wu,

652
00:28:30,180 --> 00:28:30,980
are we just going to leave now?

653
00:28:31,290 --> 00:28:32,180
Should we put in place
what you asked us

654
00:28:32,220 --> 00:28:32,730
to prepare?

655
00:28:33,570 --> 00:28:33,940
Yes, do it.

656
00:28:34,250 --> 00:28:34,570
Yes, ma'am.

657
00:28:42,050 --> 00:28:42,730
Ye Ping'an,

658
00:28:43,460 --> 00:28:45,250
you are truly audacious.

659
00:28:45,570 --> 00:28:46,700
Not only do you sell illegal salt,

660
00:28:47,220 --> 00:28:48,290
but you also secretly hoard armor.

661
00:28:48,860 --> 00:28:49,730
Such actions

662
00:28:50,050 --> 00:28:51,140
amount to treason.

663
00:28:51,700 --> 00:28:53,180
I'm just a commoner.

664
00:28:54,010 --> 00:28:55,900
How could I possibly have
this Mountain-Pattern Armor?

665
00:28:56,380 --> 00:28:57,730
Only someone from the Wu family

666
00:28:58,460 --> 00:28:59,660
would have such resources.

667
00:28:59,860 --> 00:29:00,980
You might not have the resources,

668
00:29:01,620 --> 00:29:02,900
but those behind you do.

669
00:29:03,380 --> 00:29:04,490
If the Wu family falls,

670
00:29:05,010 --> 00:29:05,940
the biggest beneficiary

671
00:29:06,250 --> 00:29:07,140
would be the Li family.

672
00:29:07,730 --> 00:29:09,050
Taking such a risk to secure

673
00:29:09,090 --> 00:29:09,940
the Crown Prince's position

674
00:29:10,570 --> 00:29:11,570
is hardly surprising.

675
00:29:11,860 --> 00:29:12,330
Enough.

676
00:29:12,770 --> 00:29:13,940
This is getting more and more absurd.

677
00:29:14,490 --> 00:29:15,530
A matter of such gravity

678
00:29:15,980 --> 00:29:17,180
cannot be determined

679
00:29:17,730 --> 00:29:18,570
by one person's words alone.

680
00:29:18,860 --> 00:29:19,330
This item

681
00:29:19,700 --> 00:29:20,900
was hidden among the illegal salt.

682
00:29:21,420 --> 00:29:21,940
No matter what,

683
00:29:21,980 --> 00:29:23,420
Ye Ping'an can't wash her hands of it.

684
00:29:23,700 --> 00:29:24,140
Someone!

685
00:29:24,980 --> 00:29:25,460
Wait!

686
00:29:26,860 --> 00:29:28,380
I'd like to see who dares
to make a move.

687
00:29:29,620 --> 00:29:30,420
Mr. Zhao,

688
00:29:31,620 --> 00:29:33,330
are you protecting Ye Ping'an

689
00:29:33,700 --> 00:29:34,250
because you, too,

690
00:29:34,940 --> 00:29:36,290
wish to commit treason?

691
00:29:38,620 --> 00:29:39,250
Mr. Zhao,

692
00:29:40,330 --> 00:29:41,010
I'll go with you.

693
00:30:00,050 --> 00:30:00,530
Over here!

694
00:30:01,380 --> 00:30:01,810
Hurry!

695
00:30:17,050 --> 00:30:17,570
You should leave now.

696
00:30:18,380 --> 00:30:18,810
Go!

697
00:30:46,250 --> 00:30:47,900
This man is Ye Ping'an's accomplice,

698
00:30:48,530 --> 00:30:50,420
Huang Yimin,
the biggest illegal salt smuggler

699
00:30:50,980 --> 00:30:51,940
in the Henan region.

700
00:30:52,420 --> 00:30:52,900
Hang on.

701
00:30:54,810 --> 00:30:55,810
Where is his crutch?

702
00:31:11,900 --> 00:31:13,700
Such a cunning act of deception.

703
00:31:13,900 --> 00:31:15,220
This matter involves many parties.

704
00:31:15,980 --> 00:31:16,700
Mr. Yuan,

705
00:31:17,290 --> 00:31:19,130
please hand the person over
to the Ministry of Justice

706
00:31:19,180 --> 00:31:20,090
for a thorough investigation.

707
00:31:20,460 --> 00:31:21,530
I captured this person,

708
00:31:22,570 --> 00:31:23,370
so naturally, the case

709
00:31:23,420 --> 00:31:24,530
should be handled
by the Court of Judicial Review.

710
00:31:25,460 --> 00:31:25,810
Mr. Yuan.

711
00:31:25,850 --> 00:31:26,570
Mr. Zhao,

712
00:31:27,460 --> 00:31:28,500
the suspect Ye Ping'an

713
00:31:28,770 --> 00:31:30,290
escaped under your watch.

714
00:31:30,810 --> 00:31:32,290
Even if it wasn't intentional,

715
00:31:32,530 --> 00:31:33,940
you are still accountable
for negligence.

716
00:31:34,810 --> 00:31:35,660
Stay out

717
00:31:36,290 --> 00:31:37,420
of this matter.

718
00:32:02,660 --> 00:32:03,130
Miss Wu.

719
00:32:03,740 --> 00:32:04,740
Zhao Feng

720
00:32:05,420 --> 00:32:06,700
once submitted a letter
to Her Majesty,

721
00:32:07,370 --> 00:32:09,090
claiming that the Crown Prince
was the rightful heir.

722
00:32:09,700 --> 00:32:10,740
Go to Xinkai Prison

723
00:32:11,130 --> 00:32:11,810
and tell Zhou Mi

724
00:32:12,330 --> 00:32:13,980
that Zhao Feng is involved
in the salt and armor case.

725
00:32:14,570 --> 00:32:15,610
Zhou Mi knows

726
00:32:16,020 --> 00:32:17,460
how to extract evidence

727
00:32:17,530 --> 00:32:18,770
from him.

728
00:32:18,810 --> 00:32:19,290
Yes, ma'am.

729
00:32:24,980 --> 00:32:27,460
The criminal Ye Ping'an
is guilty of secretly trading armor,

730
00:32:27,980 --> 00:32:30,130
resisting arrest,
and flouting the law.

731
00:32:30,420 --> 00:32:31,660
She has fled to Luozhou.

732
00:32:31,660 --> 00:32:32,700
- Luozhou.
- Luozhou.

733
00:32:32,850 --> 00:32:33,770
Anyone who reports her whereabouts

734
00:32:34,090 --> 00:32:34,900
will be rewarded
with 100 liang of silver.

735
00:32:35,530 --> 00:32:36,090
A hundred liang?

736
00:32:36,090 --> 00:32:37,660
Those who assist the authorities
in capturing her

737
00:32:38,090 --> 00:32:39,370
will be rewarded
with 1,000 liang of silver.

738
00:32:39,370 --> 00:32:40,740
[Wanted]

739
00:32:40,740 --> 00:32:42,370
Anyone found harboring her will face

740
00:32:43,290 --> 00:32:44,050
the same punishment as her.

741
00:32:44,420 --> 00:32:44,940
Why is Ye Ping'an

742
00:32:45,020 --> 00:32:45,770
involved in so many crimes?

743
00:32:45,980 --> 00:32:46,570
Indeed.

744
00:32:47,370 --> 00:32:47,810
Exactly.

745
00:32:59,500 --> 00:33:00,220
Get up.

746
00:33:01,130 --> 00:33:01,940
Quiet down.

747
00:33:02,530 --> 00:33:03,940
Someone's trying to sleep here.

748
00:33:05,370 --> 00:33:06,810
How dare you be so arrogant?

749
00:33:07,050 --> 00:33:07,980
Do you even know where you are?

750
00:33:08,370 --> 00:33:09,570
This isn't just any prison.

751
00:33:09,900 --> 00:33:10,980
This
is the Court of Judicial Review Prison.

752
00:33:11,420 --> 00:33:13,260
No matter how tough you think you are,

753
00:33:13,420 --> 00:33:13,980
here,

754
00:33:14,460 --> 00:33:15,700
you'd better bend

755
00:33:15,850 --> 00:33:16,610
and behave.

756
00:33:18,610 --> 00:33:19,900
What's your monthly salary?

757
00:33:21,940 --> 00:33:23,180
With salt costing 400 wen per dou,

758
00:33:24,090 --> 00:33:25,460
how much can you afford
with your monthly salary?

759
00:33:26,020 --> 00:33:27,570
Wait. What's that supposed to mean?

760
00:33:27,740 --> 00:33:29,220
Since you've dropped the disguise,

761
00:33:31,420 --> 00:33:33,220
stop pretending
to be an illegal salt smuggler.

762
00:33:35,610 --> 00:33:36,370
Now,

763
00:33:36,660 --> 00:33:37,770
the crime committed by Ye Ping'an

764
00:33:38,180 --> 00:33:39,850
is far worse than selling illegal salt.

765
00:33:41,180 --> 00:33:42,420
She has hoarded armor.

766
00:33:43,850 --> 00:33:45,180
According to the laws of Great Feng,

767
00:33:45,900 --> 00:33:47,130
one set of armor equals
three crossbows

768
00:33:47,850 --> 00:33:50,020
and three sets of armor
can result in execution.

769
00:33:50,900 --> 00:33:52,090
You should know this, right?

770
00:33:53,220 --> 00:33:54,500
It all leads to death anyway.

771
00:33:55,420 --> 00:33:56,500
Whether the charges are heavy or not,

772
00:33:57,610 --> 00:33:58,290
does it really matter?

773
00:33:58,980 --> 00:34:00,220
I only have two questions for you.

774
00:34:01,290 --> 00:34:01,770
First,

775
00:34:03,660 --> 00:34:05,180
what is your relationship

776
00:34:06,180 --> 00:34:07,020
with Huang Yimin?

777
00:34:10,170 --> 00:34:10,530
Second,

778
00:34:12,090 --> 00:34:13,650
where is Ye Ping'an

779
00:34:14,210 --> 00:34:15,130
right now?

780
00:34:19,210 --> 00:34:20,020
I knew

781
00:34:20,730 --> 00:34:22,570
getting an unyielding man
like you to talk

782
00:34:22,980 --> 00:34:24,130
would not be so easy,

783
00:34:25,170 --> 00:34:26,500
so I came prepared.

784
00:34:26,940 --> 00:34:28,300
How do you plan to torture me?

785
00:34:29,460 --> 00:34:30,530
Just bring it on.

786
00:34:31,530 --> 00:34:32,530
That won't be necessary.

787
00:34:33,610 --> 00:34:34,610
Your real name

788
00:34:34,940 --> 00:34:36,210
shouldn't have been traceable,

789
00:34:37,300 --> 00:34:38,730
but I still found it.

790
00:34:40,050 --> 00:34:41,090
Qiu Yin.

791
00:34:42,420 --> 00:34:43,860
You were once just a farmer,

792
00:34:44,020 --> 00:34:45,250
but you were forced into the life

793
00:34:45,300 --> 00:34:46,500
of a vagrant
when your land was taken.

794
00:34:46,940 --> 00:34:48,500
Only with the help of some friends

795
00:34:48,820 --> 00:34:50,170
did you learn martial arts,

796
00:34:50,900 --> 00:34:52,300
and become a hatchet man for a living.

797
00:34:52,650 --> 00:34:53,820
Hence, the word "loyalty"

798
00:34:54,090 --> 00:34:55,500
is etched on your heart.

799
00:35:02,210 --> 00:35:03,050
How did you find out?

800
00:35:03,570 --> 00:35:04,050
What?

801
00:35:05,340 --> 00:35:06,420
Is something I said incorrect?

802
00:35:07,210 --> 00:35:08,300
For someone like me,

803
00:35:09,940 --> 00:35:11,130
loyalty is the most important thing.

804
00:35:12,210 --> 00:35:13,570
There's no difference between friends

805
00:35:13,940 --> 00:35:14,610
and family.

806
00:35:15,090 --> 00:35:16,300
You corrupt officials

807
00:35:16,420 --> 00:35:17,300
wouldn't understand.

808
00:35:17,530 --> 00:35:18,460
Well said.

809
00:35:19,500 --> 00:35:20,980
Today, I'll see

810
00:35:21,570 --> 00:35:22,530
how you'll choose

811
00:35:23,090 --> 00:35:25,020
between friends

812
00:35:25,860 --> 00:35:26,940
and true family.

813
00:35:27,540 --> 00:35:28,740
If I remember correctly,

814
00:35:28,940 --> 00:35:29,730
you have a cousin

815
00:35:30,060 --> 00:35:31,020
in Ruanyang County.

816
00:35:32,130 --> 00:35:33,170
How about I bring him here

817
00:35:33,610 --> 00:35:34,610
to visit you?

818
00:35:34,940 --> 00:35:35,940
I'll go immediately

819
00:35:36,420 --> 00:35:37,820
and make sure he's well taken care of.

820
00:35:38,540 --> 00:35:38,860
No need.

821
00:35:43,060 --> 00:35:43,730
I can answer

822
00:35:43,820 --> 00:35:44,500
your first question.

823
00:35:47,980 --> 00:35:48,860
Over the past year,

824
00:35:50,130 --> 00:35:51,460
we've been exploring new sources of salt

825
00:35:54,420 --> 00:35:55,570
because we know

826
00:35:56,690 --> 00:35:58,050
Wu Youjing needs salt.

827
00:35:58,860 --> 00:36:00,020
How did you know

828
00:36:00,610 --> 00:36:01,900
that the Prince of Kangping

829
00:36:02,340 --> 00:36:04,650
would halt all the transportation
of salt in Yangzhou

830
00:36:05,050 --> 00:36:07,210
due to a lawsuit filed
by the local silk maker against He Yi?

831
00:36:09,530 --> 00:36:11,090
Could it be that the letter
accusing He Yi

832
00:36:11,130 --> 00:36:12,050
of embezzling the transportation fee,

833
00:36:12,570 --> 00:36:13,530
which was sent

834
00:36:13,650 --> 00:36:14,980
to the Court of Judicial Review
some time ago,

835
00:36:15,730 --> 00:36:17,650
came from Ye Ping'an?

836
00:36:20,090 --> 00:36:20,650
That's right.

837
00:36:21,900 --> 00:36:23,460
As for Huang Yimin,

838
00:36:24,060 --> 00:36:25,020
we don't really know him.

839
00:36:26,730 --> 00:36:27,980
We only borrowed his name

840
00:36:28,060 --> 00:36:28,900
because it is

841
00:36:29,170 --> 00:36:30,380
so widely recognized.

842
00:36:31,530 --> 00:36:33,300
She sure knows how to spin a good story.

843
00:36:35,860 --> 00:36:37,020
The letter of accusation

844
00:36:37,050 --> 00:36:38,380
didn't contain lies.

845
00:36:39,060 --> 00:36:40,340
As for your dear father-in-law,

846
00:36:40,730 --> 00:36:42,020
since last year,

847
00:36:42,380 --> 00:36:43,420
he's been sending people
to the salt fields

848
00:36:43,570 --> 00:36:44,860
under the pretext of capturing bandits

849
00:36:45,090 --> 00:36:46,340
and guarding the salt fields.

850
00:36:46,610 --> 00:36:47,780
He's used every possible trick

851
00:36:47,860 --> 00:36:49,170
to seize land from farmers,

852
00:36:50,650 --> 00:36:52,500
forcing many to become refugees

853
00:36:54,420 --> 00:36:56,020
and resort to selling illegal salt.

854
00:36:56,730 --> 00:36:57,380
You traitor,

855
00:36:57,730 --> 00:36:59,500
how dare you slander
the Prince of Kangping!

856
00:36:59,860 --> 00:37:00,340
Ye Ping'an...

857
00:37:06,340 --> 00:37:07,090
Tell me.

858
00:37:08,130 --> 00:37:10,380
