when he came in.

864
00:37:29,940 --> 00:37:30,530
Go fetch the physician.

865
00:37:31,460 --> 00:37:32,170
If he dies,

866
00:37:32,530 --> 00:37:33,300
I'll hold you accountable.

867
00:37:33,530 --> 00:37:33,900
Yes, sir.

868
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:41,300
[Court of Judicial Review]

869
00:37:41,340 --> 00:37:42,300
Ye Ping'an

870
00:37:42,530 --> 00:37:44,170
doesn't speak a single word of truth.

871
00:37:44,420 --> 00:37:45,050
She

872
00:37:45,380 --> 00:37:46,020
has always

873
00:37:46,050 --> 00:37:47,130
been a master of deception.

874
00:37:48,340 --> 00:37:48,900
Let's find another way

875
00:37:49,050 --> 00:37:49,820
to handle the salt issue.

876
00:37:50,820 --> 00:37:51,900
Where did you get those sets

877
00:37:54,340 --> 00:37:54,980
of Mountain-Pattern Armor?

878
00:37:55,690 --> 00:37:56,690
If you want answers, you should arrest

879
00:37:56,730 --> 00:37:57,300
and interrogate Ye Ping'an.

880
00:37:58,130 --> 00:37:59,170
She's the one

881
00:37:59,820 --> 00:38:00,530
hoarding the armor.

882
00:38:03,210 --> 00:38:05,420
You know full well
that hoarding armor is a serious crime.

883
00:38:06,060 --> 00:38:06,610
Why did you use...?

884
00:38:06,650 --> 00:38:07,860
Had it not been for the armor,

885
00:38:08,340 --> 00:38:09,020
Ye Ping'an

886
00:38:09,050 --> 00:38:10,340
could have easily explained

887
00:38:10,420 --> 00:38:11,690
the source of her salt.

888
00:38:13,650 --> 00:38:14,420
Now that she's back,

889
00:38:15,170 --> 00:38:15,860
the battle

890
00:38:16,210 --> 00:38:17,050
is on.

891
00:38:18,460 --> 00:38:19,210
This time,

892
00:38:20,130 --> 00:38:21,780
we must take her down in one fatal move.

893
00:38:26,050 --> 00:38:26,570
How is he now?

894
00:38:26,900 --> 00:38:27,860
The prisoner is in poor condition

895
00:38:28,340 --> 00:38:28,940
and unfit for interrogation.

896
00:38:29,460 --> 00:38:30,130
Investigate it!

897
00:38:31,020 --> 00:38:31,820
I'd like to see

898
00:38:32,530 --> 00:38:33,380
who dares to poison someone

899
00:38:33,460 --> 00:38:34,460
inside the Court of Judicial Review.

900
00:38:35,060 --> 00:38:35,500
Pass down my order.

901
00:38:36,340 --> 00:38:36,940
No one is to approach

902
00:38:37,530 --> 00:38:38,460
this prisoner's cell

903
00:38:38,530 --> 00:38:39,820
except for me.

904
00:38:40,820 --> 00:38:41,340
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

905
00:38:46,050 --> 00:38:46,610
Sir,

906
00:38:47,420 --> 00:38:48,020
I'd like a word

907
00:38:48,460 --> 00:38:49,050
with you in private.

908
00:38:54,020 --> 00:38:54,730
Get to the point.

909
00:38:56,500 --> 00:38:57,420
That old man

910
00:38:57,500 --> 00:38:58,780
wasn't wrong about everything.

911
00:38:59,530 --> 00:39:01,090
With the meager salary I have now,

912
00:39:03,340 --> 00:39:04,650
I can't even afford to use salt freely.

913
00:39:06,530 --> 00:39:08,020
Those are just words
meant to sow discord.

914
00:39:09,250 --> 00:39:10,020
Your salary

915
00:39:10,650 --> 00:39:11,570
might be modest,

916
00:39:12,940 --> 00:39:14,250
but hasn't the Prince of Kangping
given you

917
00:39:14,900 --> 00:39:15,980
quite a few perks under the table?

918
00:39:17,210 --> 00:39:18,210
So I guess

919
00:39:19,530 --> 00:39:20,460
I was wrong

920
00:39:20,540 --> 00:39:21,780
to expect you

921
00:39:21,860 --> 00:39:22,380
to promote me.

922
00:39:22,820 --> 00:39:24,610
I should have sided with
the Prince of Kangping from the start.

923
00:39:26,570 --> 00:39:27,050
Sir,

924
00:39:28,610 --> 00:39:29,570
do you think

925
00:39:30,130 --> 00:39:31,420
I can still change my mind now?

926
00:39:50,500 --> 00:39:51,820
This... This is the engagement gift

927
00:39:51,860 --> 00:39:53,170
the Prince of Kangping gave you.

928
00:39:53,610 --> 00:39:54,780
I wouldn't dare to take it.

929
00:39:56,570 --> 00:39:57,530
This is your reward

930
00:39:57,690 --> 00:39:59,900
once the task is done.

931
00:40:02,020 --> 00:40:02,940
I planned

932
00:40:02,980 --> 00:40:04,050
to give it to Wenyu,

933
00:40:04,300 --> 00:40:05,460
but since you are so eager for merit,

934
00:40:05,940 --> 00:40:07,420
I shall let you have it instead.

935
00:40:08,610 --> 00:40:09,210
What's the task?

936
00:40:09,780 --> 00:40:10,380
Go to Caozhou

937
00:40:11,300 --> 00:40:12,380
and find the real Huang Yimin.

938
00:40:13,050 --> 00:40:14,460
Persuade him to sell illegal salt to us.

939
00:40:15,610 --> 00:40:16,380
I've asked around

940
00:40:16,730 --> 00:40:17,980
and his salt is indeed quite cheap.

941
00:40:18,730 --> 00:40:20,020
If you can make this happen,

942
00:40:21,130 --> 00:40:22,730
you will have earned great merit for me

943
00:40:23,020 --> 00:40:24,020
in the eyes of the Prince of Kangping.

944
00:40:31,980 --> 00:40:32,530
But I have

945
00:40:32,570 --> 00:40:33,690
no connections in Caozhou.

946
00:40:33,980 --> 00:40:34,690
Even if I manage to find

947
00:40:34,730 --> 00:40:35,530
the real Huang Yimin,

948
00:40:36,050 --> 00:40:36,530
I doubt

949
00:40:36,570 --> 00:40:37,780
he'd be willing to see me.

950
00:40:38,050 --> 00:40:39,420
If I had no confidence in this,

951
00:40:39,820 --> 00:40:40,500
I wouldn't have planned

952
00:40:40,530 --> 00:40:41,860
to let Wenyu handle it.

953
00:40:43,940 --> 00:40:44,690
Open it and take a look.

954
00:40:50,650 --> 00:40:51,300
This is...

955
00:40:51,980 --> 00:40:52,530
This is the token.

956
00:40:53,050 --> 00:40:54,340
Huang Yimin, the illegal salt smuggler,

957
00:40:54,860 --> 00:40:55,460
values profit

958
00:40:56,050 --> 00:40:56,900
but cherishes loyalty even more.

959
00:40:57,130 --> 00:40:58,090
He has a son

960
00:40:58,420 --> 00:40:59,300
named Huang Qi.

961
00:41:00,460 --> 00:41:01,300
Coincidentally, I have

962
00:41:01,340 --> 00:41:02,340
a merchant friend

963
00:41:02,530 --> 00:41:03,020
who once risked his life

964
00:41:03,050 --> 00:41:04,900
to save Huang Qi
when he was being pursued

965
00:41:04,980 --> 00:41:05,780
by bandits.

966
00:41:06,380 --> 00:41:07,130
In gratitude,

967
00:41:07,170 --> 00:41:08,020
Huang Qi gave my friend

968
00:41:08,170 --> 00:41:09,300
this tooth he lost in the incident,

969
00:41:09,980 --> 00:41:10,610
promising

970
00:41:11,860 --> 00:41:13,420
to help him

971
00:41:14,210 --> 00:41:15,730
whenever needed.

972
00:41:19,610 --> 00:41:20,090
Rest assured.

973
00:41:20,530 --> 00:41:21,570
I will not let you down, sir.

974
00:41:22,210 --> 00:41:22,900
You have three days.

975
00:41:23,650 --> 00:41:24,900
Get it done, even if your horse

976
00:41:25,300 --> 00:41:26,300
collapses from exhaustion.

977
00:41:26,940 --> 00:41:27,250
Yes, sir.

978
00:42:00,620 --> 00:42:03,820
Past events turn to ash,
crushed into mud

979
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:07,250
Like a distant dream,
forever out of reach

980
00:42:07,370 --> 00:42:13,470
Your breaths faded
in silence and distance

981
00:42:13,730 --> 00:42:16,620
Thoughts form a chapter,
with a reluctant prelude

982
00:42:16,870 --> 00:42:20,520
The storm of sorrow is beyond words

983
00:42:20,670 --> 00:42:26,100
In a glance back,
no traces of the past remain

984
00:42:26,200 --> 00:42:32,900
Lost in regret,
tangled, unwritten, unspeakable

985
00:42:33,050 --> 00:42:39,700
Buried in time, too fragile to name

986
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:45,670
A cup of cold moonlight.
A page of faded tears

987
00:42:45,860 --> 00:42:52,520
Dreams, scribbled in haste,
fade into dust

988
00:42:52,580 --> 00:42:58,800
A lone wild goose cries,
echoing through the sleepless night

989
00:42:58,990 --> 00:43:06,250
Only to clutch fragments of memory
to soothe the remaining years

